    },
    {
      q: 'Does French Press always taste stronger than AeroPress?',
      a: 'It usually tastes heavier, not automatically stronger in caffeine. French Press lets more oils and fine particles into the cup, so it feels thicker and bolder on your tongue. AeroPress can still make a strong cup, but it usually tastes cleaner.',
